full_text: Screened by NARA, 5/5/2023 UNITED STATES DEPARTMENT OF JUSTICE IMMIGRATION AND NATURALIZATION SERVICE Processing Sheet Application or Petition Form No. File No. A71 833 821 DATA COLLECTION FOR ALIEN DOCUMENTATION, IDENTIFICATION & TELECOMMUNICATION SYSTEM (ADIT) Please print or type information requested below: COMPLETE NAME MARGARITA MORENO DE VIDES COMPLETE MAILING ADDRESS 563 PECKAN DR (Include Zip Code) LA PUENTE CALIFORNIA 91746 MOTHER'S FIRST NAME HIGINIA FATHER'S FIRST NAME LUIS CITY/TOWN/VILLAGE OF BIRTH SANTA ANA CITY OF RESIDENCE WHEN APPLYING FOR A VISA OR IMMIGRANT STATUS SANTA ANA CITY OF DESTINATION AT TIME OF ORIGINAL ADMISSION Los ANGELE3 LOCATION OF CONSULATE WHERE IMMIGRANT VISA SAN SALVADOR OBTAINED (OR IMMIGRATION OFFICE WHERE ADJUSTED) DATE OF BIRTH 6 5 1911 PORT OF ENTRY WHEN ADMITTED AS IMMIGRANT OR OFFICE WHERE ADJUSTED TO LAWFUL PERMANENT RESIDENT Los ANGELES SYMBOL ADMITTED UNDER (CLASSIFICATION) DATE ADMITTED OR ADJUSTED TO LAWFUL PERMANENT RESIDENT COUNTRY OF BIRTH E, SALVADOR CARD NUMBER TRANSACTION NUMBER This form may be overprinted or stamped to show instructions, items requested, items received, or other pertinent data which may facilitate processing. Keep this sheet on top of all material in file until initial decision is made. Form I-468 (ADIT) FPI-LOM (Rev. 11-1-70) 2-83 500 Tabs 5475
